{"tid":842372,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］PS4設備及遊戲黑店資料庫","createTime":"2018-09-30T09:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T05:12:46.000Z","uid":75156,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5abe66b89b7cc104772196c268402a4d15e771e3","tid":842372,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"[話說］<br />\n屌近排入手PS4唔知頭唔知路入手左黑店手制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身無拎屋企手制去對貨<br />\n係佢個度玩到拎返屋企玩到一兩日就detect路唔到<br />\n一睇背面<br />\n先知連個label都有少少野出事<br />\n返去換同佢講加錢換返個<br />\n佢話唔得都知咩事 心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己出老翻假野扮二手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 結果換個過一樣既比我又扮無事<br />\n跟本幾日之後又係無補於事<br />\n又話賣出咁多次都無人有事 講到好似我呃鳩佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵下黑店po先知咁多仆街呃人<br />\n之前賣ps4個個老闆講個陣仲以為佢講笑<br />\n二手Game扮一手都大撚把<br />\n所以想係連登開個po等大家買野個陣都唔會中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n的確係我貪平想買個二手我抵死<br />\n但都希望你我玩得放心 買樣野黎玩下唔洗戒備多多咁撚煩 Blacklist黑店免得大家中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n格式（跟編號落）<br />\n1:時間 <br />\n2:地區（地點/舖名）<br />\n3:咩設備咩game<br />\n4:類型（beta): 劏水魚/假貨/魚目混珠/etc<br />\n5:敍事+附圖<br />\n<br />\n希望各位都可以伸出仗義之手<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n杜絕黑店<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fcb3753fdab61fb61ee077ff243437d24c920b","tid":842372,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b3272f42e49b3616bb50119774dae6fdf8fa85","tid":842372,"uid":58090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5abe66b89b7cc104772196c268402a4d15e771e3","tid":842372,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"[話說］<br />\n屌近排入手PS4唔知頭唔知路