840_d29e745017023af532f423f8f2a01cb5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F171840_d29e745017023af532f423f8f2a01cb5.png&h=90bc05c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢仲話7日內有咩事可以落返黎退<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係個陣啦 就黑口黑面死狗咁款 心虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n［手制對比圖］<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/171902_1de046f672c74efcda433ed0afd01568.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F171902_1de046f672c74efcda433ed0afd01568.png&h=bec2ae29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［上圖為自家ps4手制 sony(r)圖標清晰 文字詳細 有更多詳細標示<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/172051_f99b1dd5ec24e2b9235298db180dcc40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F172051_f99b1dd5ec24e2b9235298db180dcc40.png&h=22f10157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［下圖為On9老翻 label有極大分別 商標Sony( r)十分奇怪 文字模糊］ <br />\n大家認清楚啦 <br />\n我遲d買返個新既算了"},{"pid":"2edfbba92fbdb574c9a80fadb05514ea33b1ecbf","tid":842372,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:23:02.000Z","msg":"老翻扮二手 屌你"},{"pid":"ff971817996358a56f92eb4850d1ff3324f0f67b","tid":842372,"uid":75156,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b2c0f9676edfcd85d359bc1b9bbfa88125c877c8","tid":842372,"uid":75156,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:22:37.000Z","msg":"#0001<br />\n1. 25-9-2018 買。30-9-2018 換貨。<br />\n2.深水埗 黃金11C地舖 RPG Game shop<br />\n3. 二手PS4手制$238<br />\n4.魚目混珠<br />\n5.假貨扮二手貨 用左一陣就detect唔到 充電都有問題 我估係比官方block 佢肯換返一樣既假貨比我<br />\n但唔比加錢換返個佢所謂既［行貨］$318或退貨<br />\n［收據圖］<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/171840_d29e745017023af532f423f8f2a01cb5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F20